{"tid":2258960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★iPhone 12 機背磁鐵   證實干擾機械錶機芯準確度(Omega、IWC、Breitling、Tudor...)","createTime":"2020-10-26T12:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T05:00:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8a46eaaf4e944ff044911391f41e6892a1192b","tid":2258960,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:29:20.000Z","msg":"iPhone 12 的機背內置磁吸式無線充電線圈，內裡包含了磁鐵，可以吸附 MagSafe 充電器和保護套。中國網民 @芯隨表動日前進行了測試，發現 iPhone 12 的磁鐵會干擾部份機械手錶機芯，雖然不會造成永久損壞，但就會令手錶變得走時。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n@芯隨表動量度了 iPhone 12 Pro、MagSafe 手機殼和充電器的磁力值，分別為 57 至 60 高斯、16 高斯和 123 高斯。假如用戶右手手執 iPhone 12 Pro，機械手錶戴在左手，手錶不會受到干擾。一旦 iPhone 12 Pro 或 MagSafe 配件接觸到手錶，機芯就有機會出現誤差。<br />\n@芯隨表動測試過多款機械機芯，Omega、IWC、Breitling、Tudor 等 ETA 機芯會受到明顯影響；而 Rolex、Patek Philippe、Blancpain 和 Tudor 自家開發的機芯 則不受影響。@芯隨表動以 Omega 2500 同軸蝶飛機芯作例子，指接觸 iPhone 12 Pro 或 MagSafe 配件後，原本每日誤差 1 秒會變成每天 50 秒，除非將手錶拿去消磁才能解決。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/10/25/iphone-12-magnet-mechinic-watch/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F10%2F25%2Fiphone-12-magnet-mechinic-watch%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=63de30dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/10/25/iphone-12-magnet-mechinic-watch/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"28fc5ffa01f3028e710a3f43b03991210302234a","tid":2258960,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"要求賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25969516e6e186f9370203c47bd51efac910098d","tid":2258960,"uid":18844,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:30:18.000Z","msg":"iphone咪有時間囉<br />\n手錶係裝飾品, 唔準唔緊要 <img src=\"/ass